name: Diamond Coin
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Diamond (Diamond) tokens are native to the Fantoon NFT platform, of the Pumpkittens GameFi ecosystem. It's a rare, utility driven token launched through a community LGE with Fantom's DEX SpiritSwap. Diamond tokens also introduces an emissions based LP building concept to increase the tokens expansion benefitting the community as well. Fantoon has an NFT launchpad, and various decentralised games, from all which token holders benefit. More details can be found at: https://docs.pumpkitten.com/fantoon/introducing-diamonds
